item.title: This path cannot be specified?!? PLease help!
item.dc:creator: @Ksu Ksu
item.description:
@Ksu wrote:

It is enviornmental variables. Look in your compiler (edit with notepad) and change the path to your path of Java, if you have the latest version it would be "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_20\bin\javac.exe"

or if you have 64 bit "C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jdk1.6.0_20\bin\javac.exe"
